I am marking EVERY Elite quest and dungeons as optional in this guide. Especially on release you should do them!!! You'll easily find groups for elite quests and dungeons.
If you intend to do Gun'Drak accept the next 2 quests(For Prosperity&One of a Kind). if not continue with "Eggs for Dubra'Jin"
Text: If you intend to do Gun'Drak accept the next 2 quests(For Prosperity&One of a Kind). if not continue with "Eggs for Dubra'Jin"

Name: This quest is an Elite quest and a pre-quest for the last missing Gun'Drak quest. On release you should be able to find people to do this with, later on not so much. Either way you should do Gun'Drak anyway as you got all quests for it now whilst we are moving over to Sholazar Basin now. Your last chance to find people for the missing other elite quests too. If you cant find anyone...Abandon them.
